# Belt-and-suspenders against stray tsc / convex-codegen emit artifacts
# leaking into the published tarball. The package.json `files` field is the
# primary whitelist; this file is the explicit exclude list for anything
# that would otherwise slip in (npm pack respects the package's own
# .npmignore but does NOT walk up to read the workspace-root .gitignore,
# which is where the equivalent patterns live for git-tracking purposes).
#
# Strays land in convex/*.{js,d.ts} when something runs `tsc` without
# `-p tsconfig.json --noEmit` from this directory. Convex codegen
# legitimately writes convex/_generated/{api,server}.js + *.d.ts; those
# stay shipped via the explicit `files` entry above.
convex/*.js
convex/*.d.ts
convex/*.d.ts.map
convex/helpers/*.js
convex/helpers/*.d.ts
convex/helpers/*.d.ts.map
!convex/_generated/
!convex/convex.config.ts
